original_title: Anti-government demonstrators and university students burn an effigy of Sri Lanka’s President Ranil Wickremesinghe
original_body_lines: Anti-government demonstrators and university students burn an effigy of Sri Lanka’s President Ranil Wickremesinghe and Sri Lanka’s Public Security Minister Tiran Alles while shouting slogans during a protest demanding the release of Inter University Students’ Federation leaders in Colombo on 28 April 2023 – AFP
